{"tid":417719,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Gopro 2017 發布會 (Fusion/ new drone/ Hero 6)","createTime":"2017-09-29T02:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T09:31:25.000Z","uid":51734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3ade889e0395b629b41c86cd97a437e107c022d4","tid":417719,"uid":51734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"琴晚gopro做左發布會<br />\n公布左三樣新product, 同quik app既大型更新<br />\n1. fusion <br />\n- 5.2K 360 cam<br />\n- 無死角, 最impress既係&quot;overcapture&quot; 功能, 拍完用app自己做cam man/導演 拎唔同角度做片/做相！<br />\n- 用個APP應該可以玩好多野, 睇佢DEMO片係好正<br />\n- 5米防水<br />\n- 防震 (唔知電子定光學)<br />\nHK$5,800.00 (預訂中)<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/cameras/fusion/CHDHZ-101.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.gopro.com%2FAPAC%2Fcameras%2Ffusion%2FCHDHZ-101.html&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=9a087787\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/cameras/fusion/CHDHZ-101.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. new karma drone<br />\n- 多左個follow功能, 其實dji晨早有, 死都要跟埋佢個舊karma grip, 有d失望<br />\n- HK$7,000 唔包HERO 6, HK$11,160包埋hero 6<br />\n- 包埋controller + grip<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/karmabundle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.gopro.com%2FAPAC%2Fkarmabundle&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=75d006be\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/karmabundle</a><br />\n<br />\n3. hero 6, <br />\n- 呢部係hero 5既大型upgrade<br />\n- frame rate全部double上: 4K60p, 2.7K120p, 1080K240p<br />\n- processor upgrade左唔少, dynamic range, low light都講到大大提升<br />\n- image quality睇DEMO片的確係進步左好多, 就算水底/lowlight/slowmotion都好好)<br />\n- 影到HDR <br />\n- touchscreen support埋zoom (應該都係digital zoom黎, 但用4K-2.7K, zoom左都應該好清)<br />\n- 有埋stabilizer (唔知電子定光學)<br />\n- 裸跑有10米防水<br />\n- GPS, 5GHz WiFi (快3倍), voice command upgrade, accelerometer, Bluetooth, gyroscope<br />\n- HK$3,980<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/cameras/hero6-black/CHDHX-601-master.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.gopro.com%2FAPAC%2Fcameras%2Fhero6-black%2FCHDHX-601-master.html&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=48ce8b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/cameras/hero6-black/CHDHX-601-master.html</a><br />\n<br />\n另外, 本身已經幾好用既quik (好用在易用, 重埋免費拎黎剪手機片都OK)<br />\n會出更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/experience\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.gopro.com%2FAPAC%2Fexperience&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=02d4b89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.gopro.com/APAC/experience</a><br />\n新product都會有對應既APP<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/102251_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F102251_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg&h=e0000815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n題外話: quik個desktop version廢到喊, 重要比錢先ENJOY 到APP既功能, 我用番gopro studio算 (雖然成日crash)<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n利申: hero 4 silver 用家, 心郁郁想upgrade"},{"pid":"c6f36b2b5f9de5e22faec2df1b0f958cc05cd55c","tid":417719,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:40:40.000Z","msg":"真係要睇睇hero 6影咩效果<br />\n如果唔夠好都係比sony搶客"},{"pid":"b6d435573e22a446262d16422528af5c4bb5cd3d","tid":417719,"uid":51734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係要睇睇hero 6影咩效果<br />\n如果唔夠好都係比sony搶客</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=vr0qNXmkUJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3Dvr0qNXmkUJ8&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=cb7f0015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=vr0qNXmkUJ8</a><br />\n睇呢段4K demo, 的確令我好驚喜"},{"pid":"0ab03fd4b2fe7e44dde48f50f9dfabc26814657f","tid":417719,"uid":32716,"like":0